# Crevia Frontend Overhaul — UI/UX + Production Polish

## Context
Deep frontend pass to make the app fully production-ready: premium animations, an interactive hero spotlight, notification UX fixes, a Pro verified badge system, and clear brand/creator account differentiation in the profile menu. Framer-motion is already installed (v12.23.26). ScrollReveal and HeroPattern components exist but need upgrading. The subscription hook already exposes `limits.hasVerifiedBadge` and `isPro`.

