## Feature 1 — Interactive Hero Spotlight (Cursor Pattern Reveal)

**Files:** `src/components/HeroPattern.tsx`, `src/pages/Home.tsx`

**Approach:**
- Add `spotlight?: boolean` prop to `HeroPattern`
- When `spotlight=true`, attach a `useRef` container + native `mousemove` listener
- On each move: call `el.style.setProperty('--mx', x + 'px')` and `--my` directly — zero React re-renders, 60fps
- Render a second SVG pattern layer at 3× the base opacity (the "revealed" layer)
- Mask it with: `mask-image: radial-gradient(circle 340px at var(--mx, 50%) var(--my, 50%), black 0%, transparent 100%)`
- Overlay has `pointer-events-none` — never blocks clicks
- Dark mode: reveal layer uses `text-slate-300`; light mode: `text-slate-600` — set via Tailwind `dark:` class on the SVG rect
- Reset `--mx`/`--my` to `50% 50%` on `mouseleave` for a graceful fallback
- Pass `<HeroPattern spotlight />` only in the hero section of `Home.tsx` (not the CTA HeroPattern)

