## Feature 2 — Global Animation Engine Upgrade

**Files:** `src/components/ui/ScrollReveal.tsx`, `src/index.css`

**Approach:**
- In `ScrollReveal.tsx`: upgrade easing from `[0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94]` to `[0.16, 1, 0.3, 1]` (luxury deceleration — heavy, deliberate, Apple-Stripe tier)
- Increase intersection `threshold` from `0.1` to `0.15` so animations fire when element is meaningfully in view
- Keep `once: true` default
- In `src/index.css`: upgrade `.hover-scale` and `.card-interactive` transition easing to `cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)` with `duration-500`; add a new `.animate-fade-up` keyframe with the luxury curve for hero stagger targets
- No changes needed in Home/Pricing/About — ScrollReveal is already applied; the easing upgrade flows automatically

